  "What is d/dx(4x^3 - 2x + 9)?": "d/dx( 4x_ 3 - 2x+9) 是什么?",
  "Differentiate term by term: d/dx(4x^3) = 12x^2, d/dx(-2x) = -2, and d/dx(9) = 0. So the answer is 12x^2 - 2.": "d/dx( 4x% 3) = 12x% 2, d/dx( 2x) =-2, d/dx(9) = 0。 答案是 12x% 2 - 2 。",
  "What is d/dx(sqrt(x)), rewritten as d/dx(x^(1/2))?": "d/dx(sqrt(x)),重写为d/dx(x%x(1/2))是什么?",
