  "If f(x) = x^8, what is f'(2)?": "如果f(x) = x_8, 什么是f'(2)?",
  "First find f'(x) = 8x^7 by the power rule. Then f'(2) = 8(2)^7 = 8 * 128 = 1024.": "首先根据权力规则找到 f'(x) = 8x+7。 然后f'(2) = 8(2)+7 = 8 * 128 = 1024。",
  "What is d/dx(x^(2/3))?": "d/dx(x__( 2/3))是什么?",
