  "What is the derivative of f(x) = 5x^4 + 3x^2 - x evaluated at x = 1?": "F(x) = 5x__4 + 3x__2 - x 的衍生物在 x = 1 时评价是什么?",
  "f'(x) = 20x^3 + 6x - 1. At x = 1: f'(1) = 20(1) + 6(1) - 1 = 20 + 6 - 1 = 25.": "f'(xx) = 20x3 + 6x - 1. 在x = 1: f'(1) = 20(1) + 6(1)-1 = 20+ 6-1 = 25。",
  "What is d/dx(1/x^2), rewritten as d/dx(x^(-2))?": "d/dx(1/x% 2),重写为d/dx(x%( 2))是什么?",
